                      11     
0009 08               12         INC R0            ; Next locations
000A 09               13         INC R1
000B DAF9             14         DJNZ R2, EXCHANGE
                      15     
000D 80FE             16     HERE: SJMP HERE       ; Stop
                      17     
                      18     END
